{"tid":1450593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地還拖好唔好呀？ 還拖好唔好呀？ 好唔好呀？","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:13:18.000Z","uid":159947,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"53bc7c192e64fb65d6915b6f6056f315ccd0a5c4","tid":1450593,"uid":159947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"每一次 我地人數都比起班狗多好多<br />\n但係每一次 我地都出去比人行刑<br />\n班狗既武力一次比一次都要強<br />\n我地可以頂多幾多次？<br />\n唔好再相信班狗會跟條例做野啦好嗎？<br />\n唔好再明明咁企係度做靶啦好嗎？<br />\n唔好成日諗好多好多好好既戰術然後唔用啦好嗎？<br />\n唔好老豆搵完仔然後咩都唔做啦好嗎？<br />\n唔好明知我地核彈都唔割都唔還拖啦好嗎？<br />\n究竟你地仲係度怕咩呀？<br />\n民意？唔小心打親啲狗？唔夠打？<br />\n要撐既就撐左，唔撐既就唔會撐，同溫層太耐啦。<br />\n你仲擔心啲狗安唔安全，佢有冇擔心過你安唔安全呀？<br />\n一個唔夠咪搵多幾個手足囉。<br />\n我怕我地比人就咁白白打死晒呀。<br />\n你地還拖啦，求下你地還拖啦。<br />\n我真係求下你地還拖啦。"},{"pid":"70bad3d40b80b22522bb220ec823402751cdde4d","tid":1450593,"uid":159947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"你地還拖啦"},{"pid":"c36333563d043997dd03bd3c2671e4a1145599ea","tid":1450593,"uid":159947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"還拖啦"},{"pid":"4ac038e464d3fedc9dd3103e7bee4e47ab3571b2","tid":1450593,"uid":159947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"求下你地"},{"pid":"ea8b66a0a875b2cf47451db55903b3a9bbbaf8bb","tid":1450593,"uid":159947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"還拖啦"},{"pid":"5fcf3c16074c399275d71b5f4e8883a8e5705364","tid":1450593,"uid":269975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-tWasHlig5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-tWasHlig5s&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqviVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2f0b1368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-tWasHlig5s</a>"},{"pid":"aa4e65885e23ed83ba2f1b70c74036f4cb175c63","tid":1450593,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy